<D>__{twenty five? around there.}
<C>__{adam}
<D>__{i guess living up here makes people look older.}
<C>__{bellboy}
<D>__{up here on the fifteenth floor?}
<C>__{adam}
<P>__{(catching himself)}
<D>__{yes. up here on the fifteenth floor. goodnight.}
<C>__{bellboy}
<D>__{goodnight.}
<A>__{adam abruptly shuts the door in the man's face. he goes to the window and looks out. the height scares him to death. he jumps back.}
